{"tid":1597423,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"不只一次！子瑜跳舞太激「裙子掀起來」　走光照流出","createTime":"2019-09-27T02:33:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T03:45:52.000Z","uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"585ce63c829d523f11bb07491a7839c15747725e","tid":1597423,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:33:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/1569489664-d18e5ec12290e43b3d0b76cfc7f952c0-696x435.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F1569489664-d18e5ec12290e43b3d0b76cfc7f952c0-696x435.jpg&h=eea37ca5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲子瑜演唱新歌大動作跳舞，底褲不慎走光。（圖／翻攝VLIVE）<br />\n<br />\n南韓女子天團「TWICE」23日推出全新迷你專輯《Feel Special》，發片當日，除了罹患恐慌症的Mina及彩排扭傷脖子的志效，7人穿上勁裝賣力打歌，不過或許是跳舞時動作過大，台籍成員子瑜多次被拍到露底畫面，意外成為焦點。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/1569489649-d66460f829ef668726aafeff7b460f33-1024x573.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F1569489649-d66460f829ef668726aafeff7b460f33-1024x573.png&h=735b48ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過表演時發生小插曲，「國際美人」子瑜身穿一件黑色亮片細肩洋裝，裙緣切至膝蓋上方，白皙大腿根隨舞蹈動作外露，加上攝影機由下往上取鏡，頻頻拍到女神的深色安全褲，形成另一種形式的「走光畫面」，但粉絲不以為意，依然對偶像的表現給予極高評價。（編輯：楊穎軒）<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/1569489168-551793b897cb9e8f191a1fbb647cd8fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F1569489168-551793b897cb9e8f191a1fbb647cd8fa.jpg&h=1bfd2dc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲子瑜被拍到露底畫面。（圖／翻攝xportsnews）"},{"pid":"8f35dcba296001ba3228099128ed24b52f55c502","tid":1597423,"uid":167880,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:34:29.000Z","msg":"咁都好睇？"},{"pid":"799966e3af9b7082d814687425c156113d84ab6f","tid":1597423,"uid":315091,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:41:36.000